insert into issues (summary, description) values ('An old pond, a frog jumps in, the sound of water', 'A depiction of a fleeting moment in nature, capturing the sound of a frog leaping into an ancient pond.');
insert into issues (summary, description) values ('Even when touched by autumn winds, a deeper resonance', 'Expressing a heightened sensitivity to the season of autumn, where the blowing wind evokes a profound reflection.');
insert into issues (summary, description) values ('White blooms of snow like flowers in winter, longing for the spring', 'Illustrating the winter scene where snow, resembling blossoming flowers, blankets the earth, anticipating the arrival of spring.');
insert into issues (summary, description) values ('Summer grass and soldiers are the traces of dreams', 'This is a historical haiku depicting the battle of the Tale of the Heike, and it depicts a summer landscape with lush grass, and a scene in which the images of past battles and soldiers remain as traces of dreams.');
insert into issues (summary, description) values ('The sound of cicadas that penetrates the silence and rocks', 'This haiku leaves a deep impression on the silence of summer and the sound of cicadas, expressing the sense of the seasons and the breath of nature. The sound of cicadas echoing between the rocks creates a tranquil atmosphere.');
